d to an insured System bank under this subsection if the amount of such assistance exceeds an amount determined by the Corporation to be the cost of liquidating the bank (including paying the insured obligations issued on behalf of the bank). This subparagraph shall not apply to the provision of assistance to a bank if the Corporation determines that the continued operation of the bank is essential to provide adequate agricultural credit services in the area of operations of the bank.”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(3)(B) to (F). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/105/s217/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–105, § 217(a)","children":[],"tail":", added subpars. (B) to (E) and redesignated former subpar. (B) as (F)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1990—Subsec. (f). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/624"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–624","children":[],"tail":" substituted “prior to "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1993-01-01"},"text":"January 1, 1993","children":[],"tail":"” for “beginning on the date of the enactment of this part”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1989—Subsec. (e). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/220"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–220","children":[],"tail":" inserted “and other association making direct loans under the authority provided under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s2279b"},"text":"section 2279b of this title","children":[],"tail":",” after “production credit association”."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"iddce08b73-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"iddce08b74-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":n